Masque St. Tian
collections.description: Masque St. Tian, or "Mask of Saint Sky," is an imagined glimpse of Chinese fashion through the lens of old-world French vogue. Evoking the allure of vintage fashion sketches and the ghostly presence of forgotten icons, each portrait by Tianming feels like ink bleeding through silk, an imprint left behind rather than a face fully seen. Each of the 44 unique one-of-one NFTs is a study in elegance and erosion, fragments of a forgotten era made familiar through materiality. Created using pastel and oil-based ink transfers on paper, these pieces were submitted to Orangehare.io and adapted for use as digital collectibles through in-house techniques.

collections.name: Sustained Attention Loop
collections.description:
This collection showcases images of true, authentic feelings. The feelings may be of one's past, or anticipation for one's future. Either way, the feelings these images evoke stir something deep inside each and every one of us.

A Sustained Attention Loop in art refers to a visual or conceptual mechanism that keeps the viewer engaged, continuously drawing their eye back into the artwork. It encourages prolonged observation and interaction, preventing a quick glance and instead fostering deeper contemplation.

A Sustained Attention Loop increases engagement, emotional impact, and memorability in an artwork. It prevents passive viewing and transforms an art piece into an experience, deepening the connection between the artist and the audience.

collections.name: Arte 5.0 Digital
collections.description: Un progetto innovativo e rivoluzionario nel mondo dell’arte moderna e contemporanea che attraverso un monitoraggio costante dei fermenti innovativi nei luoghi del contemporaneo dà particolare risalto alle maggiori figure protagoniste dal novecento ad oggi. Arte 5.0 si concentra a dare supporto ad artisti emergenti italiani ed internazionali, vantando un approccio innovativo basato sulla collaborazione tra galleristi, curatori e collezionisti. L’obiettivo è quello di creare intorno ai propri artisti un ambiente stimolante per la sperimentazione, la discussione e lo sviluppo del proprio lavoro. Prestando, inoltre, attenzione al rinnovamento del linguaggio artistico rimane, nel corso degli anni, al passo coi cambiamenti nel sistema dell’arte, arricchendo e diversificando le sue proposte con il fine di accompagnare i collezionisti in tutte quelle che possano essere le scelte intraprese.
